5210, "(fr)Latona Waystation has reported Combine warships heading directly for Vicare station. They will arrive within the half-hour. We've run out of time."

5211, "(fr)The composition of the attacking force is hard to pin down, but the strength of their impeller signals suggest a battlecruiser task group at least."

