5234, "(fr)I've been there before. The Children of Renewal are good people. The refugees will be well looked after."

5235, "(fr)Our job will be done once we arrive in Alliance. Once our payment comes through, I plan to find a Commonwealth port to drop off Kendra."

5236, "(fr)The Nassau, Hopewell and Flèche de Pollux are free to pick up extra contracts at Alliance to pay for running costs."

5237, "(fr)Thanks Lau. We should be fine for a while. The bonus pay promised by Reverend Lightowler is substantial. Almost unexpectedly so."

